***HELP***
**BotCommands**
warn1             <warn1 [@warnedperson] (admin only) (1st warning)
warn2             <warn2 [@warnedperson] (admin only) (2nd warning)
warn3             <warn3 [@warnedperson] (admin only) (3rd warning)
kick              <kick  [@kickedperson] (admin only) (kicks tagged member)
ban               <ban   [@bannedperson] (admin only) (bans tagged member)
flight            <flight [@hostsname]   (admin only) (Posts flight announcement)
over              <over   [@hostsname]   (admin only) (posts flight over announcement)
cancelled         <cancelled             (admin only) (cancells a flight)
help              <help                  (everyone)   (shows all the commands)
christmas         <christmas             (everyone)   (makes a christmas tree)
